OL,4,CHSBC executives to hot-desk as private
OL,5,Coffices go
OL,6, Banking giant HSBC has confirmed that
OL,7, top managers in its Canary Wharf HQ
OL,8, have lost their offices and will have
OL,9, to hot-desk on an open-plan floor.
OL,11,FThe move comes as HSBC pursues plans to
OL,12,Fshrink its office space by 40% in a
OL,13,Fpost-pandemic shake-up.
OL,15,FChief executive Noel Quinn told the
OL,16,FFinancial Times it was "the new reality
OL,17,Fof life" and that he would no longer be
OL,18,Fin the office five days a week.
OL,20,F"We don't have a designated desk. You
OL,21,Fturn up and grab one," he added.
